RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 6F Dirt CR: 73. Allowance Purse 10780. FOR NATIVE FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since June 2 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since May 17 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since April 17 Allowed 4 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CRIOLLITO led throughout. SURI BOY second best. ROU ONE ASTRAY chased, weakened. CONVINCENTE weakened. MEDIA NOCHE O. trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 6F Dirt CR: 35. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE THREE YEAR OLDS. Weight, 118 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since May 17 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since April 17 Allowed 2 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CAPTADOR vied for lead, dueled, driving. COMPASIVO bid, second best. JEY GUELIN outside, closed. DIAMOND COLLECTION pressed pace, weakened. ESPECTACULAR failed to menace. CONTROVERSIAL dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 6F Dirt CR: 41. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE JUNE 18 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: VERDADERA led throughout. ESCARAMUZA off pace, second best. CULTIVADORA stalked pace, evenly. REINA MORA chased, weakened. INFINITY BUBBLE stalked pace, weakened. ADIVINADORA dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 7F Dirt CR: 44. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR NATIVE FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON THREE RACES SINCE JUNE 17 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since June 2 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since May 17 Allo wed 2 lbs. A Race Since April 17 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: VALID BELLE pressed pace, dueled, prevailed. ECONOMICA close up, short. LUZ BRILLANTE pressed pace, gave way late. VALECAT stalked pace, gave way. JOSELYN RUBY close up, weakened. CONCEPCIONARIA improved position. SORPRESIVA failed to menace. PREJUICIOSA dropped back. MASCARILLA failed to menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 7F Dirt CR: 67. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON THREE RACES SINCE DECEMBER 17 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since June 2 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since May 17 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since April 17 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: SURF SPA led throughout. RAIZ pressed pace, second best. TAKE CHARGE AGAIN close up, good effort. MEET ME HALF WAY close up, some late gain. ROMANTIC MELODY middle of pack, some gain. HOLY SECRET weakened. ARETE'S CHALICE improved position. MICAELA D. pressed pace, weakened. LUSCIOUS improved position. BLACK LIGHTING failed to menace. OFRENDA off slowly, no menace. CHASING ZEROS did not finish.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 7F Dirt CR: 83. Claiming Purse 7500. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since June 2 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since May 17 Allowed 4 lbs. A Race Since April 17 Allowed 7 lbs. Claiming Price $14,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: THE ICE BEAST led throughout. FROLIC MAN second best. PROSPECT PROJECT improved position. DOUBLE TOUGH TIGER improved position. CHUCKY close up, weakened. END ALL GET ALL improved position. JUST CROWN failed to menace. SOLD OUT improved position. CALL BROS dropped back. THAT'S MY BOI TOY dropped back. INSPECTOR FROST refused to break.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 80. Claiming Purse 9200. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Weight, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since June 2 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since May 17 Allowed 4 lbs. A Race Since April 17 Allowed 7 lbs. Claiming Price $27,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: LOVELY DANA stalked pace, rallied, driving. STELLAR RIDE chased, second best. AUDITORA close up, evenly. ALL WHITE vied for lead, weakened. SHE'S CLASSY stalked pace, weakened. HEROICA improved position. SUNSET PAULA JO failed to menace. HUSH Y'ALL failed to menace. AMAZING TRIP dropped back. CHALLENGE PRINCESS failed to menace.
